comments.body:
sorry for not noticing this earlier. I think the `-Wno-unused-private-field` might also be leftover from some other makefile. It would be nice to remove unless it causes some issue. 

And want to add in `-fomit-frame-pointer`?

I'm going with what we have in the current cortex_m_gcc_generic_makefile.inc

I added -Wno-unused-private-field in the last commit, it is needed for:
tensorflow/lite/micro/simple_memory_allocator.h:100:18: error: private field 'error_reporter_' is not used [-Werror,-Wunused-private-field]
tensorflow/lite/micro/micro_allocator.cc:186:18: error: private field 'reporter_' is not used [-Werror,-Wunused-private-field]
Adding fomit-frame-pointer.
